[{"content":"\u003cp\u003e⚠️ Take notice: This tutorial requires a working container environment using \n  \u003ca href=\"https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\n    Docker\n  \u003c/a\u003e\n\n or \n  \u003ca href=\"https://podman.io/docs/installation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\n    Podman\n  \u003c/a\u003e\n\n.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch4 id=\"container-environment\"\u003eContainer environment\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003edocker run -it ghcr.io/thomas-bouvier/numpex-pdi-tutorial:latest\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003cp\u003eFrom within the container environment, you may test that your setup is working using the dedicated script:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e./environment_check_script\n[...]\n[0] SUCCESS \n[1] SUCCESS\n[2] SUCCESS\n[3] SUCCESS\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e","description":"","image":"/hpcasia_logo.png","permalink":"https://pdi.dev/hpcasia26/material/","title":"Material"},{"content":"\u003cdl\u003e\n\u003cdt\u003eDate:\u003c/dt\u003e\n\u003cdd\u003eJanuary 26, 2026\u003c/dd\u003e\n\u003cdt\u003eDuration:\u003c/dt\u003e\n\u003cdd\u003eFull-day\u003c/dd\u003e\n\u003cdt\u003eRoom:\u003c/dt\u003e\n\u003cdd\u003eTBD\u003c/dd\u003e\n\u003c/dl\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n      \u003ctr\u003e\n          \u003cth\u003eTime\u003c/th\u003e\n          \u003cth\u003eTopic\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n      \u003ctr\u003e\n          \u003ctd\u003e09:30-10:45\u003c/td\u003e\n          \u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSession 1\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIntroduction to PDI and environment setup \u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHands-on\u003c/strong\u003e: Instrument your code with PDI\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003c/tr\u003e\n      \u003ctr\u003e\n          \u003ctd\u003e10:45–11:15\u003c/td\u003e\n          \u003ctd\u003eCoffee Break\u003c/